dreams have pretty much faded at this point.

824
01:05:20,554 --> 01:05:21,578
Faded.

825
01:05:21,869 --> 01:05:23,698
Treasure the experience.

826
01:05:23,751 --> 01:05:26,291
Dreams eventually will fade away.

827
01:05:27,190 --> 01:05:29,695
I went through similar times myself,

828
01:05:29,945 --> 01:05:31,658
and so did your mother.

829
01:05:33,091 --> 01:05:36,512
