as his daughter, I can convince him.

878
01:08:05,481 --> 01:08:06,810
It's the perfect plan.

879
01:08:08,618 --> 01:08:10,980
Fine, I don't really care one way or the other.

880
01:08:11,286 --> 01:08:13,128
This is just a theory of yours, right?

881
01:08:13,561 --> 01:08:15,623
Uh. Well...

882
01:08:15,776 --> 01:08:17,373
Theories can be based on reality!

883
01:08:17,480 --> 01:08:19,986
Like, do you know the story of
how Itomori Lake was formed?

884
01:08:20,170 --> 01:08:21,318
It's a crater!

885
01:08:21,534 --> 01:08:25,498
That means a meteor hit this area
at least once a thousand years ago!

886
01:08:25,790 --> 01:08:27,503
