899
01:09:21,750 --> 01:09:22,601
You!

900
01:09:24,499 --> 01:09:25,734
You son of a...

901
01:09:34,379 --> 01:09:35,241
Mitsuha?

902
01:09:36,876 --> 01:09:37,658
No...

903
01:09:38,769 --> 01:09:39,863
Wait a minute...

904
01:09:41,559 --> 01:09:42,430
Who are you?

905
01:09:57,897 --> 01:09:59,263
I'll see you guys at the festival.

906
01:09:59,288 --> 01:10:01,715
We'll meet you at the steps to the shrine!
Don't be late, okay?

907
01:10:01,740 --> 01:10:02,569
Bye-bye!

908
01:10:02,594 --> 01:10:03,156
See ya.

909
01:10:03,249 --> 01:10:04,049
Later.

910
01:10:05,851 --> 01:10:06,971
You shouldn't go!

911
01:10:07,601 --> 01:10:10,154
You've gotta leave town! Tell all of your friends!

912
01:10:10,180 --> 01:10:11,606
What's wrong with ya?

913
01:10:11,762 --> 01:10:12,576
Mitsuha!

914
01:10:12,600 --> 01:10:13,586
What was that about?

915
01:10:13,610 --> 01:10:14,828
Come on. Let's go.

916
01:10:15,210 --> 01:10:17,249
What're you doing, huh?

917
01:10:17,903 --> 01:10:19,216
If it was Mitsuha,

918
01:10:19,858 --> 01:10:21,891
would she have been able to convince him?

919
01:10:22,196 --> 01:10:23,572
Is all this my fault?

920
01:10:24,037 --> 01:10:27,614
Yotsuha! Promise me that you'll
leave town with Grandma before dark!

921
01:10:27,880 --> 01:10:28,405
What?

922
01:10:28,518 --> 01:10:30,172
You're gonna die if you stay here!

923
01:10:30,224 --> 01:10:31,487
What're you talking about?

924
01:10:31,599 --> 01:10:34,109
And why'd you suddenly go to Tokyo yesterday?

925
01:10:34,134 --> 01:10:36,595
You've been acting really strange lately!

926
01:10:38,190 --> 01:10:39,517
Went to Tokyo?

927
01:10:39,686 --> 01:10:42,121
Hey, Mitsuha!

928
01:10:44,530 --> 01:10:45,966
How'd it go with your old man?

929
01:10:48,643 --> 01:10:50,326
Hey! Mitsuha!

930
01:10:51,163 --> 01:10:52,559
What's with your sister?

931
01:10:52,727 --> 01:10:53,776
Dunno.

932
01:11:04,020 --> 01:11:05,614
Could she be over there?

933
01:11:06,440 --> 01:11:08,568
What's that? What's over there?

934
01:11:09,110 --> 01:11:10,665
Let me use your bike, Teshi.

935
01:11:10,770 --> 01:11:13,149
Hey! Mitsuha!

936
01:11:14,260 --> 01:11:15,526
And what do we do?

937
01:11:15,937 --> 01:11:17,690
Get things ready like we planned!

938
01:11:18,160 --> 01:11:19,447
I'm counting on you!

939
01:11:46,239 --> 01:11:48,338
Oh my gosh! I'm Taki again.

940
01:11:51,423 --> 01:11:53,868
But what was Taki doing out here?

941
01:12:03,493 --> 01:12:04,424
The town...

942
01:12:05,193 --> 01:12:06,856
It's gone.

943
01:12:16,505 --> 01:12:19,575
So does that mean...

944
01:12:22,186 --> 01:12:24,013
...they died?

945
01:12:34,613 --> 01:12:35,586
Taki.

946
01:12:36,433 --> 01:12:37,275
Taki!

947
01:12:40,020 --> 01:12:41,523
Don't you remember?

948
01:12:54,340 --> 01:12:56,220
I'm going to Tokyo for a few hours.

949
01:12:56,542 --> 01:12:57,915
What? Right now?

950
01:12:58,388 --> 01:12:59,284
