951
01:12:59,693 --> 01:13:00,485
For a date.

952
01:13:01,099 --> 01:13:03,083
You have a boyfriend in Tokyo?

953
01:13:03,108 --> 01:13:05,217
I didn't say it was a date for me.

954
01:13:06,437 --> 01:13:07,997
I'll be back tonight.

955
01:13:11,373 --> 01:13:12,760
If I suddenly show up,

956
01:13:12,907 --> 01:13:16,177
will it be a nuisance? Or a surprise?

957
01:13:16,941 --> 01:13:18,765
He might not like it if I do.

958
01:13:26,850 --> 01:13:30,860
The number you are trying to reach is
currently outside the cellular network.

959
01:13:31,230 --> 01:13:32,801
I guess it won't happen.

960
01:13:33,536 --> 01:13:35,604
But what if it did?

961
01:13:36,484 --> 01:13:39,552
What would I do? Would I annoy him?

962
01:13:40,465 --> 01:13:41,787
Would it be awkward?

963
01:13:42,450 --> 01:13:46,517
Or maybe... he'd be glad to see me.

964
01:13:48,183 --> 01:13:51,840
The number you are trying to reach is
currently outside the cellular network.

965
01:13:53,210 --> 01:13:54,857
I guess we won't meet.

966
01:13:56,879 --> 01:13:57,410
But...

967
01:13:58,573 --> 01:14:00,893
...there's one thing I'm certain of.

968
01:14:02,280 --> 01:14:03,716
If we see each other,

969
01:14:04,263 --> 01:14:06,546
we'll definitely know right away.

970
01:14:07,675 --> 01:14:10,275
That you were the one who was in me.

971
01:14:11,520 --> 01:14:15,377
And that I was the one that was in you.

972
01:14:15,404 --> 01:14:15,853
Sorry.

973
01:14:19,325 --> 01:14:23,180
The train will be arriving momentarily.
Please stand behind the line.

974
01:14:23,680 --> 01:14:27,006
When entering the train, please mind the gap.

975
01:14:47,630 --> 01:14:48,627
Excuse me.

976
01:14:48,767 --> 01:14:51,206
The doors are now closing.

977
01:15:21,363 --> 01:15:25,415
That time three years ago, before I even knew you...

978
01:15:25,440 --> 01:15:28,638
Yotsuya. The platform will be on the right.

979
01:15:29,392 --> 01:15:30,319
Taki.

980
01:15:31,630 --> 01:15:32,759
Taki.

981
01:15:34,676 --> 01:15:35,634
Taki.

982
01:15:37,109 --> 01:15:39,002
Um, it's me!

983
01:15:41,579 --> 01:15:43,718
Don't you remember?

984
01:15:45,021 --> 01:15:46,513
Sorry, who are you?

985
01:15:51,274 --> 01:15:52,541
I-I'm sorry.

986
01:16:00,450 --> 01:16:01,820
But he's Taki.

987
01:16:03,519 --> 01:16:04,773
What a weird girl.

988
01:16:04,990 --> 01:16:09,067
Yotsuya. Yotsuya. Stand clear of the doors.

989
01:16:13,910 --> 01:16:14,653
Hold on!

990
01:16:15,482 --> 01:16:17,116
But what's your name?

991
01:16:18,377 --> 01:16:19,278
Mitsuha!

992
01:16:19,692 --> 01:16:22,294
My name is... Mitsuha!

993
01:16:28,934 --> 01:16:32,034
Three years ago, you showed up.

994
01:16:33,135 --> 01:16:35,924
It was... to see me!

995
01:16:47,523 --> 01:16:48,287
Taki?

996
01:16:57,525 --> 01:16:59,150
Mitsuha!

997
01:17:00,223 --> 01:17:00,975
Taki!?

998
01:17:16,138 --> 01:17:17,511
Mitsuha!

999
01:17:18,215 --> 01:17:21,872
You're here, right? Inside my body!

1000
01:17:22,386 --> 01:17:23,297
Taki!

1001
01:17:24,695 --> 01:17:25,893
Taki, where are you?

1002
01:17:26,981 --> 01:17:27,989
That was Mitsuha.

1003
01:17:29,118 --> 01:17:30,798
I can hear her voice, but...

1004
01:17:31,940 --> 01:17:34,368
Taki, where are you?

1005
01:17:35,162 --> 01:17:36,182
Taki!

1006
01:17:49,599 --> 01:17:51,856
Taki, are you...?

1007
01:17:52,505 --> 01:17:54,059
Are you there?

1008
01:18:19,716 --> 01:18:20,782
Magic hour.

1009
01:18:35,759 --> 01:18:36,828
Mitsuha.

1010
01:18:43,479 --> 01:18:44,410
Taki.

1011
01:18:45,763 --> 01:18:46,565
Taki!

1012
01:18:47,400 --> 01:18:48,720
You're really here.

1013
01:18:53,470 --> 01:18:54,618
Taki!

1014
01:18:54,742 --> 01:18:56,413
I came all this way to see you.

1015
01:18:57,130 --> 01:18:58,495
Which wasn't easy,

1016
01:18:58,728 --> 01:19:00,870
since you were pretty far away.

1017
01:19:02,110 --> 01:19:03,749
Huh? How is that even...?

1018
01:19:04,340 --> 01:19:05,957
Because back then...

1019
01:19:06,183 --> 01:19:08,543
Well, I drank some of your <i>kuchikamizake</i>.

1020
01:19:12,820 --> 01:19:14,617
You... You drank that?

1021
01:19:15,841 --> 01:19:17,358
Stupid pervert!

1022
01:19:17,383 --> 01:19:18,069
Wh-What?

1023
01:19:18,210 --> 01:19:19,220
Yeah! That's right!

1024
01:19:19,230 --> 01:19:21,802
You were touching my boobies, weren't you?

1025
01:19:21,970 --> 01:19:23,475
Wh...?! H-How do you even...?

1026
01:19:23,490 --> 01:19:24,882
'Cause Yotsuha saw you!

1027
01:19:24,907 --> 01:19:28,865
I-I just... I couldn't help myself!
But it was just the one time.

1028
01:19:28,890 --> 01:19:30,397
Just the one time?

1029
01:19:32,199 --> 01:19:34,665
